\title{reach.io: Hydrometric Data Pipeline Tools for the Environment Agency API}
\description{
A hydrometric data pipeline toolkit covering the full journey from raw EA
data sources through to partitioned Parquet Bronze storage.

A hydrometric data pipeline toolkit for the Environment Agency Hydrology API \url{https://environment.data.gov.uk/hydrology/doc/reference}. Provides tools to query and download rainfall, flow, and water level data via synchronous and batch methods; build and maintain a master gauge registry; route gauge fetches to the correct source system (HDE, WISKI, or bulk file); ingest historical bulk files into partitioned Parquet (Bronze tier); and orchestrate parallelised backfills across thousands of gauges with per-gauge logging and failure recovery.
}
